+```
+src/
+  db.ts          - Database connection + schema initialization
+  ot.ts          - Operational Transform types + transform function
+  documents.ts   - Document CRUD repository (wraps DB)
+  room.ts        - DocumentRoom: in-memory session state per document
+  routes.ts      - Express REST routes
+  server.ts      - createApp factory (HTTP + WebSocket wiring)
+  tests/
+    ot.test.ts         - OT transform logic
+    documents.test.ts  - DB repository
+    routes.test.ts     - REST API integration tests
+    collab.test.ts     - WebSocket collaboration + concurrency tests
+```
+
